CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, Philadelphia edition, May 11, 1940, pg. 15 reads: "A.M.E.'s Open General Conference In Detroit - No. 7 - Rev. Joseph Gomez and Rev. Allen shake hands while other delegates look on"
TitMainTitle: Reverend Joseph Gomez, seated and shaking hands with Reverend Allen while other delegates look on in Ebenezer AME Church during AME General Conference, Detroit
